videos.description: Jake Bentley tosses a 2-yard touchdown to former walk-on Jacob August.
videos.headline: Bentley finds TE for 2-yard South Carolina TD

videos.description: Jake Bentley finds a wide-open Kyle Markway for a 19-yard TD pass.
videos.headline: South Carolina takes 14-0 lead on TD pass

videos.description: Lamical Perine finds some room and pushes his way in for a 2-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Florida's Perine pushes in for 2-yard TD

videos.description: South Carolina retakes the lead on a leaping 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Jake Bentley leaps for 1-yard TD

videos.description: David Reese drops the punt and it is recovered by South Carolina to set up great field position.
videos.headline: Florida's David Reese muffs punt

videos.description: With South Carolina backed up on its own goal line, Deebo Samuel takes a slant for an 89-yard catch and run but doesn't score.
videos.headline: Samuel outruns almost everyone on 89-yard catch

videos.description: Feleipe Franks slings a screen to Kadarius Toney for an 18-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Toney takes screen pass 18 yards for TD

videos.description: Lamical Perine cuts and runs for a 23-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Perine zigs his way for Gators TD

videos.description: Florida storms back to take the lead on a touchdown run by Feleipe Franks after trailing 31-14 vs. South Carolina.
videos.headline: Franks dives on fourth down for go-ahead TD
